Steps to deploy to GCP Cloud Run:
docker build -t
gcloud artifacts repositories create YOUR_REPO_NAME --repository-format=docker --location=YOUR_REGION --description="Docker repository for hello world
gcloud auth configure-docker us-east4-docker.pkg.dev
docker tag
docker push
gcloud run deploy hello-world-service --image YOUR_REGION-docker.pkg.dev/YOUR_PROJECT_ID/YOUR_REPO_NAME/hello-world:latest --platform managed --region YOUR_REGION


